citations:
    citation-agot-catelyn-ii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Catelyn II"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Catelyn. Ned and Catelyn discuss whether to accept the Handship. Maester Luwin is called; Ned decides to accept and go south. Plans are made: Catelyn stays at Winterfell with Robb and Rickon; Ned takes Arya, Sansa, and Bran south; Jon goes with Benjen to the Wall."
